00:07:49,286 --> 00:07:51,019
                         No way.

201
00:07:51,054 --> 00:07:52,287
              But losing is part
            of being a champion,

202
00:07:52,322 --> 00:07:55,190
              and you have to be
   a good sport, no matter what.

203
00:07:55,225 --> 00:07:58,994
            ♪ Little Miss Piggy,
           you've got a little ♪

